article_id:41,category_name:News,title_name:About the Summon Showcase update,image_path:,message:<div>The Summon Showcase will be updated at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539756000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Please note that while the 5★ appearance rates increase if no 5★ is summoned 10 times in a row, this increase will not carry over once the Summon Showcase is updated.</div><div><br></div><div>For more details on the appearance rates, please check the steps below:</div><div><br></div><div>[1] Tap the &quot;Summon&quot; icon at the bottom of the main screen</div><div>[2] Tap the &quot;Showcase Info&quot; button in the center right side of the screen</div><div>[3] Tap the &quot;Details&quot; tab at the top of the Showcase Info screen</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1539747000,update_time1542363527